# You do NOT need any of these for normal use.
# Claude Code (claude -p) and Codex CLI (codex exec) authenticate via your Max / ChatGPT
# SUBSCRIPTIONS — no API key, no per-token billing. The default LLM match (`--red claude
# --blue codex`) uses those subscriptions.
#
# Set the variables below ONLY if you want the optional billed REST paths
# (the `anthropic-api` / `openai-api` commanders), e.g. for high-throughput batch matches.

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=    # OPTIONAL. WARNING: if set, `claude -p` bills as API, not your Max sub.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=       # OPTIONAL. Billed per token.

# For headless/CI use of the Claude subscription (no browser), mint a 1-year token:
#   claude setup-token   ->   export CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=...
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# Model overrides for the optional REST API commanders
# MIAOSUAN_ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
# MIAOSUAN_OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5.5
